SummaryEnglish: The once beautiful and luxurious Planet Kelpar is now dry and on the brink of death after its precocious Kar-Lalo plant, known throughout the galaxy as a major source for super energy, was exploited by Earthlings to extinction. Now, three intrepid space children: Axel, Jono and Gaga want to rebuild their desolate planet following the ancient legend of the lost oasis of Kar-Lalo.
